extras_big/07e6fa359bc84d607e6ab61b3753d425.avif?t=1774875169 width=1560 height=662 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark comedy meets adult visual novel</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple branching paths and endings </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dignity/Cuck/Chaos point system affecting story outcomes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Self-aware satirical writing with cringe-humor elements</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Road trip progression through increasingly absurd locations</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4134900/extras/7c4389ebe60e5e9f36a91162eedc6ad1.avif?t=1774875169\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4134900/extras_big/7c4389ebe60e5e9f36a91162eedc6ad1.avif?t=1774875169 width=1560 height=662 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience over 20 <strong>(4 available in Demo)</strong> meticulously crafted intimate scenes with fluid frame-by-frame animation. From steamy motel mishaps to breakdown-side encounters, each situation is brought to life through detailed artwork that balances raunchy comedy with genuine heat.</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4134900/extras/e7f132343e0aee2b238d6c7f214ad3d6.avif?t=1774875169\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4134900/extras_big/e7f132343e0aee2b238d6c7f214ad3d6.avif?t=1774875169 width=1560 height=662 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Broken RV, A Disastrous Road Trip:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can You Survive the Ultimate Test of Your Dignity?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_